ne, refusing to leave his home and the orchard he had been cultivating all his life. Even at the cost of risking his life", "short_description": "So what happened . Humans Happened. Water politics paralyze the region while issues remain unresolved, the sea\u2019s water levels continue to disappear rapidly, 35 meters in 35 years. As this ecological disaster leaves in its wake a fragile landscape, it also dramatically reshapes people\u2019s lives."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vTB9QkEglEoGWqRiiejtmGluAKDptYFAgijYU1fjypF3J8n1QQQVWJ1R5-_1hUzRkqSCDwaxKOhSJew/pub", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Blimey TV", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://blimey.tv/blog/welcome-to-our-blog-but-what-is-it", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["DOCUMENTARY_HISTORY", "EDUCATIONAL", "TRAVEL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "476233047407103"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974613_1618094888527989_1872741332558645297_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bu05pjYEGfcQ7kNvgFiXTcH&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAHD8ltQg8gFDN3tqmYh-QGBkPmCVkaOcjS99slX7LiNw&oe=670D14C3"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Once Upon a Sea - Shimon Shukron -